jcurses.event

Class ItemListenerManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • jcurses.event.ListenerManager
      • jcurses.event.ItemListenerManager

  • public class ItemListenerManager
extends ListenerManager
    This class implements a listener manager to manage jcurses.event.ItemEvent instances and listener on these. Only possible type of handled events is jcurses.event.ItemEvent, of managed listeners id jcurses.event.ItemListener
